      "acceptanceCriteria": "SQA plan documented; version control, regression testing, and change management demonstrated for all three FEA codes (FDA in-house, Ansys 2022R2, DePuy Synthes internal solver).",
      "rationale": "All three modeling environments operate under documented SQA frameworks. FDA in-house code is maintained under a formal configuration management system with regression test suites. Ansys 2022R2 is a commercially validated platform with published V&V documentation. DePuy Synthes internal solver is governed by a 21 CFR Part 11-compliant quality system. Version hashes recorded in study record. Gradation 3 achieved."
