      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Code verification benchmarks (patch test, single-element tests, published NAFEMS benchmarks) passed for all element types used in the pedicle screw mesh.",
      "rationale": "Hexahedral and tetrahedral element formulations verified against NAFEMS LE1, LE3, and LE10 benchmarks. Contact algorithm verified against Hertzian contact analytical solution. All benchmarks pass within 1% of reference solution. Gradation 3 achieved."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
