      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Constitutive model selection justified by literature and sensitivity analysis; geometric fidelity of screw thread and rod interface documented.",
      "rationale": "Bilinear isotropic hardening plasticity adopted for Ti-6Al-4V screw and rod based on published coupon test data (n=6 specimens per lot). Sensitivity analysis shows QoI changes <3% when tangent modulus varied ±20%. Screw thread geometry reproduced from manufacturer CAD to within 0.01 mm tolerance. Gradation 3 achieved."
    },
    {
