      "rationale": "Young's modulus, yield strength, and ultimate tensile strength measured from six tensile coupons per material lot (screw and rod). Geometric dimensions of each of the 11 test constructs measured by CMM prior to testing; as-measured dimensions used in corresponding FEA models. Input uncertainty propagated via Monte Carlo (n=1000) yielding 95% prediction interval on stiffness of ±4.1%. Gradation 3 achieved."
    },
    {
