      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "acceptanceCriteria": "FEA inputs matched to as-tested specimen geometry and material properties; correspondence table provided for each of 11 constructs.",
      "rationale": "A specimen-specific correspondence table maps each of the 11 physical constructs to its corresponding FEA model instance, including as-measured CMM geometry, lot-specific material properties, and recorded test machine compliance correction. No surrogate or nominal values substituted for any specimen-specific parameter. Gradation 3 achieved."
    },
    {
