      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative comparison metric (E/uval) computed for each QoI; all metrics within pre-specified acceptance bounds; statistical significance assessed.",
      "rationale": "E/uval computed for stiffness (0.87), yield force (1.41), and force at 40 mm (1.55); all below the pre-specified threshold of 1.96. Mean absolute percent errors of 4.2%, 6.8%, and 7.1% respectively, all below the 10% bound. Bland-Altman plots confirm no systematic bias. Inter-laboratory variability assessed; Lab A and Lab B results statistically indistinguishable (Levene p=0.43). Gradation 3 achieved."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
